      <title>中国瞄准保证金贷款和卖空以帮助稳定股市</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-targets-margin-loans-short-selling-help-stabilise-stocks-2024-02-05/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国证监会周一表示，将加强对融资融券、恶意卖空行为的监管，防范质押股票风险。]]></description>
