    <item>
      <title>分析师预计稀土价格将在 2024 年下半年反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/rare-earths-prices-seen-rebounding-second-half-2024-analysts-2024-02-05/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[分析师表示，稀土价格可能已经触底，并有望在今年晚些时候上涨，因为电动汽车和风电的需求以及主要生产国中国预计将取消扩大的产量配额。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/rare-earths-prices-seen-rebounding-second-half-2024-analysts-2024-02-05/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 12:55:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>工作忧虑让中国人回家度假心情不好</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/job-worries-sour-mood-chinese-heading-home-holidays-2024-02-05/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，中国工人们挤上火车回家过农历新年假期，他们对工作和经济不景气的担忧给人们期待已久的家庭团聚蒙上了阴影。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/job-worries-sour-mood-chinese-heading-home-holidays-2024-02-05/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 12:31:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>杨恒均：这句话对中澳关系意味着什么</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-harsh-sentence-australian-writer-tests-limits-rebound-ties-2024-02-05/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[分析人士表示，澳大利亚作家杨恒均周一在北京被判处死刑缓期执行，这不太可能破坏澳中关系，但将考验堪培拉在多年紧张关系后推动两国关系重回正轨的努力的极限。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-harsh-sentence-australian-writer-tests-limits-rebound-ties-2024-02-05/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 12:24:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>独家：随着股市暴跌，中国券商限制跨境互换--消息人士</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-brokers-restrict-cross-border-swaps-stocks-plunge-sources-2024-02-05/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据六位知情人士透露，包括国有巨头中国国际金融公司（中金公司）在内的中国券商已限制国内投资者可以进行的跨境掉期交易金额，因为当局试图捍卫疲软的股市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-brokers-restrict-cross-border-swaps-stocks-plunge-sources-2024-02-05/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 12:20:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚人杨恒均在中国被判处死刑缓期执行，他是一位富有魅力的博主、间谍小说家</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/yang-hengjun-australian-given-suspended-death-sentence-china-was-charismatic-2024-02-05/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚博主杨恒均周一在北京一家法院出庭，因间谍罪名被判处死刑缓期执行，他在悉尼的朋友说，他看起来“非常瘦弱，非常脆弱”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/yang-hengjun-australian-given-suspended-death-sentence-china-was-charismatic-2024-02-05/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 12:04:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>雅诗兰黛因中国需求不稳定而裁员；股价飙升19%</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/estee-lauder-slashes-annual-profit-forecast-cut-jobs-2024-02-05/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[化妆品巨头雅诗兰黛计划在全球裁员 3% 至 5%，因为这家化妆品巨头加大了努力，以提高因中国客户削减高价奢侈品而受到挤压的利润率，导致其股价上涨高达 19%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/estee-lauder-slashes-annual-profit-forecast-cut-jobs-2024-02-05/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 11:49:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>独家：AI芯片需求迫使华为放缓智能手机生产</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/ai-chip-demand-forces-huawei-slow-smartphone-production-sources-2024-02-05/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对华为人工智能芯片的需求飙升，加上制造限制，迫使这家中国科技巨头优先考虑人工智能，并放慢了其高端 Mate 60 手机的生产速度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/ai-chip-demand-forces-huawei-slow-smartphone-production-sources-2024-02-05/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 08:56:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
